summary: A driven data management and engineering professional with fifteen years’ experience encompassing both onsite and office positions related to data management, geosciences and engineering.  A disciplined self-starter who quickly adapts to working in teams or alone. Intermediate user of subsurface, drilling, and data management tools. Exposure to wellsite work and acquisition of wireline data.
